(3) A person who fails to comply with the provisions of subsection (2), or who produces a document kept for the purposes thereof which is to his knowledge false in a material particular, shall be guilty of an offence and shall be liable to a fine not exceeding three thousand penalty units or to imprisonment for a term not exceeding three months or to both. [As amended by Act No. 13 of 1994 ]
